en_627192_0	The Bakmaha Divuruma organized on behalf of a drugs free country will be given on the day after tomorrow.
en_627192_1	The function will be held under the patronage of President Maithripala Sirisena.
en_627192_2	The prime purpose of the event is to rally the people against the use of drugs.
en_627192_3	The Bak Maha Divurama will take place on Wednesday the 03rd, with the participation of school children countrywide and the active contribution of heads and employees of all State, Corporation and Statutory Boards representing national, provincial, district and regional levels.
en_627192_4	Arrangements have been made to hold the function at the Colombo Independence Square under the auspices of President Maithripala Sirisena at 8.30 am.
en_627192_5	The Government has invited everyone to give this pledge on the same day at the same time in its effort to make the country free from drugs.
